CompanyDescription.label: Company Description
CompanyDescription.value: AirNet Technology Inc provides in-flight solutions to connectivity, entertainment, and digital multimedia in China. It offers Internet connections through a network of satellites and land-based beacons, provides airline travelers with interactive entertainment, and breaking news, and furnishes corporate clients with advertisements tailored to the perceptions of the travelers.
